== 美国在危地马拉的政策目标 ==
[[File:President_Trump_Delivers_Remarks_on_Asylum_(48414419007).jpg|thumb]]
美国国务院列出了在危地马拉的政策目标，包括:
*支持民主制度化和执行《和平协定》;
*鼓励尊重人权和法治，并在危地马拉执行打击有罪不罚现象国际委员会(CICIG);
*支持基础广泛的经济增长和可持续发展，维持互利的贸易和商业关系，包括确保中美洲自由贸易区和发展战略惠及危地马拉民众的所有阶层;
*合作打击洗钱、贪污、贩毒、偷运外国人及其他跨国犯罪;
*通过支持解决边界/领土争端支持中美洲一体化。<ref name=USSD/>

2019年7月15日，危地马拉总统吉米·莫拉莱斯取消了与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的会面，此前危地马拉最高法院对特朗普政府限制进入美国的瓜地马拉移民数量的政策目标发出禁止令。<ref name=cbsguat>{{Cite web | url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/migrants-at-border-guatemala-cancels-president-jimmy-morales-meeting-donald-trump-today-safe-country-2019-07-15/ | title=Guatemala cancels leader's meeting with Trump as court mulls "safe third country" status for asylum seekers | access-date=2020-08-01 | archive-date=2020-11-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126120323/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/migrants-at-border-guatemala-cancels-president-jimmy-morales-meeting-donald-trump-today-safe-country-2019-07-15/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=migrantsguat>{{Cite web|url = https://theglobepost.com/2019/07/15/guatemala-migration-deal-us/|title = Guatemala Court Blocks Signing of Migration Deal with US|date = 2019-07-15|access-date = 2020-08-01|archive-date = 2020-09-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200927194106/https://theglobepost.com/2019/07/15/guatemala-migration-deal-us/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.democracynow.org/2019/7/15/headlines/guatemala_cancels_meeting_with_trump_as_court_halts_contested_migration_deal | title=Guatemala Cancels Meeting with Trump as Court Halts Contested Migration Deal | access-date=2020-08-01 | archive-date=2020-11-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108002050/https://www.democracynow.org/2019/7/15/headlines/guatemala_cancels_meeting_with_trump_as_court_halts_contested_migration_deal | dead-url=no }}</ref>

